<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="27">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hong-zhen-yu-59" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hong-zhen-yu-59" class="zg-link" title="洪阵雨">洪阵雨</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xuge-ge" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xuge-ge" class="zg-link" title="xu哥哥">xu哥哥</a></span>
